  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2cbaeec8dbe84e069925173ac3a6210b, type: 3}
  m_Name: Dlg_Forest_GM_Finale
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ElementalAlchemist.Dialogue.DialogueData
  _speaker: Grand Master
  _lines:
  - So the Guardian found you worthy. Well done. You are no longer a novice, but an apprentice.
  - With the breath of life, recipes that once led nowhere will bear fruit. Refined elements are within your reach now.
  - Explore, experiment, and when you are ready, descend to the Underground. Your journey has only begun.
